{"tid":1609683,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大J有tips !!!","createTime":"2019-10-01T15:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T17:19:40.000Z","uid":238656,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"528fa63b54ee154d0da4eb06ee0c443ecb0d20c8","tid":1609683,"uid":238656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:11:52.000Z","msg":"話説今日下午玩online game，有好多玩家用太空坦克係度射射射。射還射，你都要明白呢個遊戲有樣野叫射程。<br />\n<br />\n敵人係你射程以外，就唔好係又射，唔係又射啦.... 浪費子彈兼浪費自己AP，而家D online game又下下都要課金買道具架嘛...<br />\n<br />\n仲有，有D玩家9射都算，唔好盲射team kill射到我吖... 好彩射中我既係墨汁炮無乜殺傷力，不過我個角色就多左個水墨畫skin囉... 瞄準D啊下次！<br />\n<br />\n雖然我就仲係玩緊記錄模式，實戰模式仲未解鎖既，不過都想講多兩句。<br />\n1，太空坦克高射炮，45度角向上先係最遠射程！今日D玩家下下都水平2~30度角射，邊射得遠呢？<br />\n2，射之前確認下前面目標方向，有時候會有D NPC角色係敵人附近，射中會扣分，所以小心D射<br />\n<br />\n係咁多。<br />\n<br />\n#明就明<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eh356Tf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Feh356Tf.png&h=12f01c22&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8e10038e12006b737e4f87137a7a031bb250628","tid":1609683,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:12:15.000Z","msg":"葵涌要人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1609533\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1609533</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2459b9ced81afd9d0fc214570b1e191021328af7","tid":1609683,"uid":326804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:12:25.000Z","msg":"10.1分水嶺里程碑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1609669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1609669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f24abcd77eb23aa2174d817fdcdbd4f455180bf1","tid":1609683,"uid":238656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:13:04.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"5a01fcdbe6bdc073fd002cf0475cfa7f16d32497","tid":1609683,"uid":238656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:13:48.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"dbcbf6686d48bcfb46780474469b436119139b53","tid":1609683,"uid":294052,"like":0,"dislike"